Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.22,0:01:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?泰勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.89,0:01:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經很飽啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.29,0:01:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  阿薩琳難得邀請我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.29,0:01:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看她很快樂的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.97,0:01:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開朗的陛下  我也第一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薩琳是乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.91,0:02:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.95,0:02:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎?\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.65,0:02:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?  那就多採點吧  來幫忙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以問一件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.03,0:02:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.33,0:02:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下為什麼要寵愛泰勒呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.27,0:02:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和八哥八哥在一起時  覺得無憂無慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.68,0:02:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!阿薩琳呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.88,0:02:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無憂無慮…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.69,0:02:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後部  破損率百分之十二!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣下去會被幹掉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.36,0:03:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方又同是惑星聯合宇宙軍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.70,0:03:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該反擊呢?還是不該反擊呢?\N這才是問題!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.01,0:03:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面的命令絕對遵守  連自己人也攻擊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.05,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方小行星群正在接近!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.39,0:03:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.35,0:03:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要迴避就必須降低航行速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.36,0:03:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做就會遭到狙擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.36,0:03:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦好呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.00,0:03:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如是泰勒的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.74,0:03:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如是艦長的話會怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如是…艦長的話…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.42,0:03:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!全速前進!\N就這樣衝進小行星群裡面吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.76,0:03:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和小行星撞擊的話就完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒撞擊到就沒事啦!全速前進!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了…了解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.73,0:04:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.41,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥  肚子會很痛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.45,0:04:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像比剛才好一點的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥\N不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來  結果怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.79,0:04:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問了醫療班  他們說無法治好泰勒的病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.43,0:04:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?八哥八哥是我的寵物呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.13,0:04:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒是和我們不同的種族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.47,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為生態機能不一樣  無法治療
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…\N不要緊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是吃太多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥  要什麼東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會痛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.12,0:05:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有萬一  我會很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下的心被泰勒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.00,0:05:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從小行星群脫離了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.47,0:05:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!這樣的話就算是他們\N也無法追來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為會發生什麼事呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們運氣還不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的好運  不會再有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.11,0:05:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!要去搭救艦長啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.52,0:05:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快確認拉爾康主力艦隊的位置吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.55,0:05:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主力艦隊的位置…?\N副艦長你不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.86,0:05:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用微風號的爛雷達…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要囉哩囉嗦  妳就趕快做吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了…了解  副艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.87,0:05:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉爾康主力艦隊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看!我說的不會錯吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人艦隊  消失了  很可能是使用雷達波隔絕系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,位置的記錄呢?\N當然保持著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.52,0:06:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!那麼現在開始超越時空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.12,0:06:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超越時空?\N可是如果超越時空時  馬上會遭到攻擊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.06,0:06:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和敵人艦隊座標重疊的話  因量子爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連空間都會消失也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.17,0:06:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣  一定要去搭救艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊!只好憑男子漢的義氣!做一決勝負!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山本上尉…看起來好像泰勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然超越時空嗎?山本這傢伙也會亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.91,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為泰勒不在後  也許會正常一點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.25,0:06:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長不負責任  所以連副艦長也不負責任嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.16,0:06:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於要開始實戰了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭救泰勒大人只是時間問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.60,0:06:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!艦長不在了\N現在連副艦長也這個樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只好好好的幹囉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.24,0:07:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一開始就在好好的幹呀  對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…請你平安無事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.88,0:07:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題  春美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.28,0:07:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長這個人…\N現在也許在吃拉爾康好吃的東西也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.62,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來喝酒放輕鬆一點  這樣對身體比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超越時空準備OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超越時空開始!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.16,0:07:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人驅逐艦在第三十八區畫面上出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.59,0:07:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接近本艦!\N接近本艦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.26,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長!  敵人反擊之前  快下救出命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一刻都不能猶豫!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上組成敢死隊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.64,0:08:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為救出艦長要衝進敵艦裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的船員  準備應付敵人的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要緊跟著我!知道了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.69,0:08:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲!\N敵襲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.86,0:08:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的突襲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.29,0:08:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…這種失態  是我離開不在時發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切責任…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.67,0:08:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更要緊的是現在應該先把阿薩琳\N隱藏在安全地方才要緊  不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.04,0:08:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.71,0:08:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快陪陛下到安全的地方!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下  請把一切事情交給我旺克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥  肚子還會痛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像好多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射干擾雷達金屬箔條!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人不只一艘  接近到下方全域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改用戰鬥機攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.75,0:09:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嵐風號  蜃龍號出發\N三十妙內  內火艇也會出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.42,0:09:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們上了干擾金屬箔條的當  用戰鬥機來應戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.42,0:09:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為使安特森們船艦容易移動  發出煙幕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現龐大傢伙之前  把艦長救出!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛美  由美  等一下要畫擊落標示時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為免發生困難  把擊落的敵機要好好記下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解!\N我不會輸的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奉副艦長命令送來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運氣好的話  肉搏戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.14,0:10:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好就變成太空的塵埃囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.41,0:10:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內火艇  出發準備好了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!出發!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始要衝入了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.45,0:10:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有在敵艦艦內肉搏戰啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.16,0:10:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要怕呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.63,0:11:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.97,0:11:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然向梅爾巴攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惑星聯合宇宙軍也有相當的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥  你知道是誰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的!究竟是誰呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒  陛下就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.10,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  要去敲敲敵人的心臟部位喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安特森  對他們不必用敲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃我這個!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上囉!傢伙們!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像衝入成功的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.32,0:12:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題是在救出艦長之前  這艘微風號還能不能維持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.49,0:12:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算救出  能不能回去還不知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.49,0:12:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  一定會有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長如果在這裡  他一定這樣回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧?上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.83,0:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯!盡人事而聽天命!\N這就是戰爭的奧妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多的數目!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳傢伙!現在是佩服的時候嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡連一步都不能再讓你們前進!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.53,0:13:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.17,0:13:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是避難用的房間  我以為只提供躲避的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.54,0:13:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  好豪華啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這地方就沒有問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.54,0:13:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更要緊的  肚子的情況呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.71,0:13:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托阿薩琳的福  好像沒有事呦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好  八哥八哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是還有以後的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.55,0:13:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會交代特姆儘快把你們的醫生請來到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.52,0:13:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是都是些奇妙的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.22,0:13:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是進貢的東西  是各星球的民俗藝品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是很昂貴的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是都是俗不可耐的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽聽我的意見好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.92,0:14:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到帝國會這麼早就落在我的手裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.86,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下呀  妳和父親一樣會遭到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.46,0:14:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惑星聯合宇宙軍的毒手而丟掉性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機關室中彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.61,0:14:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超越時空系統被破壞了  不能馬上使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.51,0:14:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超越時空不能使用  這樣的話  救出艦長也逃不出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.58,0:14:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要輕易放棄!\N『一定會有辦法吧』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.22,0:14:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如是艦長  一定會這麼說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?妳說要和我商量?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在說出以前  你要答應我不告訴任何人好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.30,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就答應妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎?那我就說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.24,0:15:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.64,0:15:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是很久以來一位老朋友的苦惱\N這位老朋友她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像第一次喜歡上男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔!妳的那位朋友…叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多的秘密呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密就是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.33,0:15:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  然後呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.33,0:15:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那位男人和我朋友不管怎麼樣  是無法結合的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.67,0:15:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就太可憐了  也許是年齡差距太大?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.67,0:15:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好敏銳啊  八哥八哥這也是原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.67,0:15:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話  還有其他理由嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.68,0:15:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了!是否叫羅密歐和什麼的\N雙方父母是仇人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.98,0:15:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許意思有一點不同  這也是原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.02,0:15:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有嗎?那就是身份差得這麼的遠?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這也是原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.70,0:16:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的理由究竟是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後的理由是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.03,0:16:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後的理由是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…\N那是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.34,0:16:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方的那個男人  非常的遲鈍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.71,0:16:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遲鈍?常會有這樣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.25,0:16:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到這裡還不懂嗎?八哥八哥\N我對你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭八哥八哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.39,0:16:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.73,0:16:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦!皇帝陛下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發…發生了什麼事?八哥八哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.43,0:17:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛睜開呀!把眼睛睜開呀!怎麼啦?八哥八哥\N我說的話聽不見嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.81,0:17:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.48,0:18:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛睜開呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.15,0:18:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  為什麼不回答?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.17,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.19,0:18:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.86,0:18:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.03,0:18:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!連動都不能動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.84,0:19:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?他們為什麼不發射過來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.05,0:19:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥他…\N八哥八哥他救了我的命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆  去轉告大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就要和八哥八哥一起到敵艦裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.50,0:19:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這梅爾巴不能拯救八哥八哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.92,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要告訴八哥八哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這事交代好  我一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.93,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.54,0:20:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是神聖拉爾康帝國皇帝戈撒十六世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.94,0:20:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就帶我到你們的艦裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳是皇帝?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪不會發射過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.97,0:20:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會失敗…\N可恨的是那個泰勒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.58,0:20:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒你要活下去  活著代替我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護陛下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.00,0:21:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就要開始動手術\N手術刀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.66,0:21:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.53,0:21:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以死喔
